### Courses API
### Base URL: /api/v1/data/courses/

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/data

### Get all published courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/ HTTP/1.1

### Get course by UUID
# Replace with actual UUID from the list response
@courseUuid = ab704909-8661-4f1b-8d90-0ee430323c4d

GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseUuid}}/ HTTP/1.1

### Get non-existent course (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/ HTTP/1.1
